Name: ID
Description: This is a unique identifying number for the pair of AIS transmissions described by the following data.

Name: MMSI_x
Description: This is the Maritime Mobile Service Identity of the first vessel.

Name: BaseDateTime_x
Description: This is the time of the first vessel's AIS transmission.

Name: LAT_x
Description: This is the latitude of the first vessel.

Name: LON_x
Description: This is the longitude of the first vessel.

Name: SOG_x
Description: This is the speed over ground for the first vessel.

Name: COG_x
Description: This is the course over ground for the first vessel.

Name: Heading_x
Description: This is the heading of the first vessel.

Name: VesselName_x
Description: This is the name of the first vessel.

Name: IMO_x
Description: This is the IMO number of the first vessel.

Name: CallSign_x
Description: This is the call sign of the first vessel.

Name: VesselType_x
Description: This is the vessel type for the first vessel.

Name: Status_x
Description: This is the status of the first vessel.

Name: Length_x
Description: This is the length of the first vessel.

Name: Width_x
Description: This is the width of the first vessel.

Name: Draft_x
Description: This is the draft of the first vessel.

Name: Cargo_x
Description: This is the cargo code of the first vessel.

Name: MMSI_y
Description: This is the Maritime Mobile Service Identity of the second vessel.

Name: BaseDateTime_y
Description: This is the time of the second vessel's AIS transmission.

Name: LAT_y
Description: This is the latitude of the second vessel.

Name: LON_y
Description: This is the longitude of the second vessel.

Name: SOG_y
Description: This is the speed over ground for the second vessel.

Name: COG_y
Description: This is the course over ground for the second vessel.

Name: Heading_y
Description: This is the heading of second vessel.

Name: VesselName_y
Description: This is the name of the second vessel.

Name: IMO_y
Description: This is the second vessel's IMO number.

Name: CallSign_y
Description: This is the second vessel's call sign.

Name: VesselType_y
Description: This is the second vessel's vessel type.

Name: Status_y
Description: This is the second vessel's status.

Name: Length_y
Description: This is the second vessel's length.

Name: Width_y
Description: This is the second vessel's width.

Name: Draft_y
Description: This is the second vessel's draft.

Name: Cargo_y
Description: This is the second vessel's cargo code.
